title: Tech wins seventh-straight, defeats Iowa - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech wins seventh-straight, defeats Iowa - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: IOWA CITY, Iowa – The No. 17 Texas Tech baseball team won its series opener at Iowa, 11-3, on Saturday afternoon at Duane Banks Field. The series was scheduled to get underway on Friday, but weather forced the nonconference pairing into a two-game series that will wrap up on Sunday at 1 p.m.
